| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0711 — Recovery Inhibition (clop)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 05ea7230-b6a0-5df9-b98f-79e3be6a6d6d"
